The frontend is a react app with vite, styled with Tailwind v4, and uses shadcn/ui for components.

It should be structured as follows

my-react-app/
├── public/
│   ├── assets/
│   └── favicon.ico
├── src/
│   ├── components/
│   ├── layouts/
│   ├── pages/
│   ├── hooks/
│   ├── api/
│   ├── App.jsx
│   ├── main.jsx
│   └── index.css
├── .env
├── vite.config.js
└── package.json


Use shadcn for basic components and shadcn-chat for any chat components

React components should be called like chat-message-list.tsx